<section class="asyle-journal-all py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center journal-intro">
      
      <div class="col-lg-6 text-center">
        <img src="images/universityimg2.png" alt="Journal Submission"  />
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="section-title mb-4">
          <h3>Asyle Data Solution</h3>
          <h2>Journal Submission & Academic Publication Support</h2>
          <p>
            Comprehensive support for Journal Articles, Research Papers, Book Chapters, and Conference Publications –
            Simplifying the Path to Academic Success
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="intro-content">
          <p>
            Publishing in peer-reviewed, high-impact journals is essential for advancing
            scientific knowledge and establishing academic or professional credibility.
            Complex submission systems, strict guidelines, and tight deadlines can be overwhelming.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Asyle</strong> offers end-to-end support for all types of academic publications:
            journal articles, conference papers, book chapters, and more. Our expert team handles everything
            from manuscript preparation to post-publication promotion.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row g-4 mb-5 journal-services-gap">

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">📝</span>
          <h4>Manuscript Preparation</h4>
          <p>Consistency, clarity, conciseness, formatting per journal guidelines, figures & tables preparation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">✏️</span>
          <h4>Editing & Proofreading</h4>
          <p>Language accuracy, polished professional voice, style consistency, grammar & reference checking.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">🔍</span>
          <h4>Journal Selection</h4>
          <p>Scope, audience, impact factor, indexing, open access options, and timelines considered for optimal fit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">👥</span>
          <h4>Peer Review Assistance</h4>
          <p>Reviewer identification, response guidance, revision tracking, and rebuttal drafting support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">📤</span>
          <h4>Submission Management</h4>
          <p>Cover letter preparation, submission platform handling, metadata entry, and timely tracking of submissions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">⚖️</span>
          <h4>Compliance & Regulatory Guidance</h4>
          <p>Authorship, ethical approvals, conflict of interest, copyright, data sharing, and research ethics compliance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">🌐</span>
          <h4>Post-Publication Support</h4>
          <p>Promotion, dissemination, indexing support, citations tracking, and author queries management.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">🎯</span>
          <h4>Customized Solutions</h4>
          <p>Strategic planning, collaborative approach, and tailored solutions for journal or book submissions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">📊</span>
          <h4>Data Collection & Analysis</h4>
          <p>Survey design, statistical analysis, SPSS/R/Python processing, and visualization support for manuscripts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">📑</span>
          <h4>Article Publication Support</h4>
          <p>Assistance with formatting, copyright, submission, and communication with editors until acceptance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">📚</span>
          <h4>Book / Chapter Publication</h4>
          <p>Support for book proposals, chapter submissions, editor communication, and academic publishing guidelines.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
        <div class="layer-card">
          <span class="icon">🎤</span>
          <h4>Conference & Workshop Submission</h4>
          <p>Abstract preparation, poster & presentation guidance, and submission handling for conferences and workshops.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>


    <div class="who-we-serve mb-5">
      <h3>Who We Serve</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Academic Researchers & Scientists</li>
        <li>Pharmaceutical & Biotech Companies</li>
        <li>Clinical Trial Teams & CROs</li>
        <li>Medical Device & Diagnostics Companies</li>
        <li>Universities, Hospitals & Research Institutions</li>
        <li>Postgraduate & PhD Students</li>
        <li>Conference & Workshop Organizers</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="process mb-5">
      <h3>How Our Publication Support Works</h3>

      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step"><span>1</span> Share finalized manuscript / data / article / book chapter</div>
        <div class="step"><span>2</span> Editing, formatting & cover letter preparation</div>
        <div class="step"><span>3</span> Journal / publisher selection & submission</div>
        <div class="step"><span>4</span> Peer review management & revision support</div>
        <div class="step"><span>5</span> Proof of submission, tracking, and follow-up until acceptance</div>
        <div class="step"><span>6</span> Post-publication promotion, indexing, and citation management</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="benefits-wrapper mb-5">
      <div class="benefits-content">
        <h3>Why Choose Asyle?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>End-to-end publication support – journals, books, conferences</li>
          <li>Experienced team with domain-specific expertise</li>
          <li>Time-saving, allowing researchers to focus on science</li>
          <li>Transparent communication & submission tracking</li>
          <li>High acceptance and publication success rate</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-image">
        <img src="images/abt_img.png" alt="Why Choose Asyle">
      </div>
    </div>

